high_descs: Turn right to the fridge, then right to the coffee machine.
Pick up a potato from the counter.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Take the potato to the left at the end of the island near the trash can.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a potato and put it in the trash.

high_descs: Turn to your right and head towards the refrigerator, once there turn right and continue walking until you reach the coffee maker.
Pick up the potato behind the coffee mug, on the counter top.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave that is just above the stove.
Place the potato in the microwave, heat it, then remove the potato from the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the end of the kitchen island, then turn left again by the black garbage can on the floor .
Put the heated potato in the garbage can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the garbage can on the floor, next to the kitchen Island.

high_descs: Go right and the right again to face the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Pick the potato up from the counter.
Go left and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the potato up and shut the door.
Go left and turn around to the left to face the trash can on the floor in front of the counter.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed potato in the trash can.
